{"tid":1607321,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日係前排既兄弟入一入","createTime":"2019-09-30T19:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T20:19:28.000Z","uid":62609,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8ecc02cf4c58d7eeb0e5dd56267eb5ba3a4b6c","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:48:36.000Z","msg":"無論聽日係點，你地都係後面人既膽，因為後面其實睇唔到前面咩情況。所以如果你地衝，後面既人會跟住衝。相反如果你哋走，後面都會跟住退，仲會散得好快。。<br />\n<br />\n我喺度諗如果前面見到狗，慢慢行。。係大約一百米時向前沖鋒，我相信後面d 人都會跟住你衝。我覺得就算係長盾陣，只要夠膽衝我估都可以衝到過去。<br />\n<br />\n總好過對峙之後比時間d 狗慢慢部署。。<br />\n<br />\n利申，唔夠膽做第一個衝，但有人做第一個我就夠膽做第二個"},{"pid":"2d49826a0309fad483f53e4eed78575adc7557e8","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:48:55.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8eaf779b48f5cb13e62745b564288bd0ad4e7293","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:49:06.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"57e757273d64e28e6a011f286e5bea0e0a830719","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:49:20.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2cea714ad19cdf9801016d0c350be2ed20c7ad44","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:49:31.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"de98f3ae283bd34e1f03443958df867fc5ef3ab8","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:49:42.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"bd1256b6f89246171828d72fe1a4efd3b1548637","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:49:52.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"416715aa59a95f8a5ca722429b8825bed391d227","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:50:02.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"7259bd46a70e311b430f8552a5f2a4dcde87d580","tid":1607321,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:50:16.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"8407ce221bed9d9899861b605985319040c4af